{"tid":1260142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好多人好著重灰衫警\"fact check\"","createTime":"2019-06-26T18:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T19:29:58.000Z","uid":52023,"like":25,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b1a7f7da4cda68d348601ca84dc229f7acf48a","tid":1260142,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T18:25:17.000Z","msg":"第一 <br />\n關於fact 唔fact check<br />\n唔喺現場其實做唔到啲咩 <br />\n有線條片已經好撚清楚<br />\n唔喺現場上網得個講字嘅叫人睇返條片就得<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n睇完嘅人鍾意講乜就講乜 <br />\n睇嗰個人點理解其實係唔到你管<br />\n有人鍾意夾硬唔理有線條片陳述自然就唔會有人信<br />\n唔到你話你講咗就係抹黑咗件事<br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n俾位人入論係完全唔撚會成立<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">就算</span></strong>灰衫真係煽動示威者 <br />\nTVB一樣可以輕鬆剪條片俾藍屍打飛機再自行陳述<br />\n要用呢個理由做你根本從來都唔洗有位入<br />\n唔好ON9講咩俾位入<br />\n根本由612開始日日都入緊你哋班示威者日日搞事"},{"pid":"283a5cc6ef910431b51494e772875e9c968d5cc6","tid":1260142,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T18:26:39.000Z","msg":"話便衣畀示威者發現 先衝入狗總<br />\n有冇人可以證明唔係特登？<br />\n之前咁多便衣都冇事 點解佢就會有事？？<br />\n再引人追住佢上樓 <br />\n之後班狗就開閘打人"},{"pid":"5dcc299374c9c7d6d1bc200167effd4dd51368e3","tid":1260142,"uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T18:28:14.000Z","msg":"1. fact check撚可唔可以fact check埋梁烈唯有冇去遊行？<br />\n2. 有另一單女警facebook教唆示威者衝擊，你們可以去跟進依單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1259950/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1259950/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"cda14cd943a252940ceb2d901f08551583e8bb5d","tid":1260142,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T18:28:36.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\n有線條Link<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1143617942496939?s=591185662&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1143617942496939%3Fs%3D591185662%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=d3e119e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/1